{"id":1,"name":"EV001","note":"","pages":[{"conditions":{"actorId":1,"actorValid":false,"itemId":1,"itemValid":false,"selfSwitchCh":"A","selfSwitchValid":false,"switch1Id":1,"switch1Valid":false,"switch2Id":1,"switch2Valid":false,"variableId":1,"variableValid":false,"variableValue":0},"directionFix":false,"image":{"characterIndex":0,"characterName":"","direction":2,"pattern":0,"tileId":0},"list":[{"code":241,"indent":0,"parameters":[{"name":"Worldbearer Matirx","volume":90,"pitch":100,"pan":0}]},{"code":121,"indent":0,"parameters":[3,3,0]},{"code":211,"indent":0,"parameters":[0]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"control intro",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"black",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,1]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["玩前提示："]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["是只做好了框架的测试版，详情看更新日志"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["有问题统统记下来，打完后统一找作者算账（？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",2,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>能听到吗？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",2,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>……敌？悬锋……漠斯？醒醒——"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["……"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",2,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>哎呀……难不成真的要我手动分离……"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>白厄？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>呀？醒了吗！"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>抱歉呀，人家不是你心心念念的救世主。真不好意思突然把你唤醒。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>？迷迷？不对，昔涟小姐？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>什么时候再创世？这是哪？你要我做什么？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>……呀，万敌还真是一如既往地直接。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>你可以把这里当成某人记忆的迷宫。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>我的伙伴正在赶来，而我正在为最后一次再创世做准备。却发现你的记忆和另一人的忆质缠在一起，分不开。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>如果不把这团乱码整理好，之后再创世可能会出问题。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>我不敢强行把你们分离，又叫不醒属于另一个人的意识……所以人家就把你喊醒，试试看你能不能从内部解开它。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>总感觉类似的事情不久前发生过一次……"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>这片空间，很脆弱。我甚至可以直接——"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>哎哎哎等一下等一下！！"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>如你所述，这片忆质确实很脆弱，所以才得更加小心翼翼。为此人家特别强调——"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>绝对不能在这里战斗！而是要智取！"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["……"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>你让纷争半神，智取记忆迷宫。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",1,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>我可没忘记，你在这一轮回是智种学派毕业的。智取某颗智种里发芽的迷宫，没问题的！"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>那你大概也没忘，为了对抗来古士，我让阿那克萨戈拉斯把我的脑子卸了。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",1,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>我没忘，所以我唤醒的是还没被裂魂的你！而且我也会帮你的，我能在外部查资料！"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mydei",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>算了。先从哪里开始？"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["mem",1,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>深呼吸，潜入他的迷宫吧。"]},{"code":211,"indent":0,"parameters":[1]},{"code":242,"indent":0,"parameters":[10]},{"code":201,"indent":0,"parameters":[0,3,6,5,0,0]},{"code":0,"indent":0,"parameters":[]}],"moveFrequency":3,"moveRoute":{"list":[{"code":0,"parameters":[]}],"repeat":true,"skippable":false,"wait":false},"moveSpeed":3,"moveType":0,"priorityType":0,"stepAnime":false,"through":false,"trigger":4,"walkAnime":true}],"x":0,"y":0}
]
}